        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/20685\">#20685</a> adds <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Real.rpow#doc\">docs#Real.rpow</a> versions of four lemmas that exist for <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=NNReal.rpow#doc\">docs#NNReal.rpow</a> and <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=ENNReal.rpow#doc\">docs#ENNReal.rpow</a> .</p>",
